comments: Conley (UTA) makes contact with the ball and incidental contact with Paul's (OKC) hand on the ball.
Schroder (OKC) establishes his right foot as his pivot foot, and then moves it before releasing the pass.
Adams (OKC) sets the screen in Conley's (UTA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Conley (UTA) makes contact with Paul's (OKC) arm during the rip-through.  The contact occurs before Paul begins his upward shooting motion.
O'Neale (UTA) sets the pick in Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path and does not prevent him from disengaging from the contact.
Adams (OKC) sets the screen in Mitchell's (UTA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Ingles (UTA) and Adams (OKC) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
O'Neale (UTA) sets the pick in Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path and does not deliver contact.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) makes marginal contact with Mitchell (UTA) as he disengages from the contact.
Adams (OKC) makes marginal contact with Gobert (UTA) before he contests the shot attempt.
Gobert (UTA) makes contact to the arm of Adams (OKC) during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Gobert (UTA) sets the pick in Diallo's (OKC) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Mitchell (UTA) makes incidental contact with Gallinari (OKC) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) and Conley (UTA) briefly engage and separate off ball.
Gallinari (OKC) extends his arm into Conley's (UTA) body and affects his SQBR.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) makes marginal contact with Ingles (UTA) during his drive.
Diallo (OKC) moves laterally into the path of Mitchell (UTA) on the drive and the contact affects his SQBR.
Gobert (UTA) is not in a legal guarding position when contact occurs with Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) that affects his driving shot attempt.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) commits a take foul on Conley (UTA).
Paul (OKC) and Mitchell (UTA) make incidental contact with one another during the inbound pass.
